  "title": "Locum, Wellness Centre",
  "description": "<p>The NUH Wellness Centre provides evidence based health screening services and primary care to our non-subsidized patients, including international patients. We are seeking experienced physicians with a strong background in primary care to join us as Locums.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>As a Locum, you shall be responsible for the consultation of both local and international patients for health screening at the NUH Wellness Centre. Your key responsibilities will include (not limited to):</p>\n<p>•           Physical Examination &amp; History Taking</p>\n<p>•           Conduct pap smears for female</p>\n<p>•           Verify results in CPSS</p>\n<p>•           Medical review of results</p>\n<p>•           Provide referral letters</p>\n<p>•           Prepare medical reports</p>\n<p>•           Other medical services such as prescriptions, medical advices</p>",
